mizedReason\": \"\",\n30:       \"reactionGroups\": [],\n31:       \"url\": \"https://github.com/obophenotype/uberon/pull/3531#issuecomment-2895838467\",\n32:       \"viewerDidAuthor\": true\n33:     },\n34:     {\n35:       \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAAidd86smv8w\",\n36:       \"author\": {\n37:         \"login\": \"cmungall\"\n38:       },\n39:       \"authorAssociation\": \"MEMBER\",\n40:       \"body\": \"After examining the Uberon ontology, I found that the correct syntax for seeAlso entries is:\\n\\nproperty_value: seeAlso \\\"URL\\\" xsd:anyURI\\n\\nFor example:\\n- property_value: seeAlso \\\"https://github.com/obophenotype/uberon/issues/457\\\" xsd:anyURI\\n- property_value: seeAlso \\\"http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/uberon/docs/The-axial-skeleton\\\" xsd:anyURI\\n\\nWhen referencing other ontology terms:\\nproperty_value: seeAlso \\\"TERM_ID\\\" xsd:string\\n\\nFor example:\\n- property_value: seeAlso \\\"GO:0007592\\\" xsd:string\\n- property_value: seeAlso \\\"UBERON:0012254\\\" xsd:string {notes=\\\"abdominal aorta artery\\\"}\\n\\nYou can also add optional notes to provide context.\\n\\nSigned by @dragon-ai-agent\",\n41:       \"createdAt\": \"2025-05-20T21:09:57Z\",\n42:       \"includesCreatedEdit\": false,\n43:       \"isMinimized\": false,\n44:       \"minimizedReason\": \"\",\n45:       \"reactionGroups\": [],\n46:       \"url\": \"https://github.com/obophenotype/uberon/pull/3531#issuecomment-2895839024\",\n47:       \"viewerDidAuthor\": true\n48:     }\n49:   ],\n50:   \"title\": \"Add COB alignment comment and see_also link to UBERON:0000000\",\n51:   \"url\": \"https://github.com/obophenotype/uberon/pull/3531\"\n52: }\n\n(End of file - total 52 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"{\n  \"body\": \"Fixes #3530\\n\\nAs requested, I've added a comment to UBERON:0000000 stating that the term is being aligned with COB, and added a see_also link to https://github.com/OBOFoundry/COB/issues/51.\\n\\n@dragon-ai-agent\",\n  \"comments\": [\n    {\n      \"id